{
  "stem": "11089.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I used to go in the back, always, a little short.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They used to give me bread to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't-- I didn't have too much left, because if people saw the bread, they attacked me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was left a few crumbs in my palm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had soldiers-- German soldiers from Romania-- it was occupied by the Germans-- who used to say to us, be smart.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Take it easy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Don't work too hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But if you see the Germans are coming with the dogs, start working.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were sitting underneath a bush, and we were watching.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we saw the Germans are coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We started to say, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so they jumped up, those soldiers with the rifles, and they started to yell at us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So people are people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when people turn into animals-- and those German SS, and the Gestapo, they were trained for years to be void of any human feelings.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to them, a human being was nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Those people, I hate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But otherwise, why should I hate people?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why should people suffer, like I suffered?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I don't hate Germans, or anybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I hate killers, robbers, murderers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Many of these children that you speak to, have-- have they heard about the Holocaust, what happened during the Second World War?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yep.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- the Jewish mostly did, because they still have many grandparents or so, relatives.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And many of us who is telling the stories, even though I know that the same proportion probably do not tell-- which I think, to my opinion, it's wrong.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They should tell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I don't want to go into this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But for example, I remember last speaking, what I did was, in Kipling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A whole class, grade 15, all black people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The whole class.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
